	end

	A -->|doCreate / doRead / doUpdate / doDelete| B
	B -->|setProvider MySQL| C
	C -->|SQL + Parameters| D
	D -->|Settings| E
	E -->|Coerced Config| F
	F -->|TCP Connections| G

